 "transcript": [
  {
   "start": 0.0,
   "end": 3.92,
   "text": "Well, there's no cars down here at all."
  },
  {
   "start": 8.18,
   "end": 10.06,
   "text": "We can go back here and have a closer look at the belt."
  },
  {
   "start": 10.36,
   "end": 10.96,
   "text": "Oh, cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 12.4,
   "end": 14.74,
   "text": "Well, people tend to think that this is the old one"
  },
  {
   "start": 14.74,
   "end": 17.72,
   "text": "Because it's made of steel and it has this rust on it."
  },
  {
   "start": 17.9,
   "end": 20.4,
   "text": "But actually, this is the new one from 1955."
  },
  {
   "start": 20.86,
   "end": 21.38,
   "text": "Oh, okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 21.72,
   "end": 22.64,
   "text": "So that's not old."
  },
  {
   "start": 23.5,
   "end": 26.6,
   "text": "These are from 1685, these two."
  },
  {
   "start": 26.6,
   "end": 27.22,
   "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
   "start": 27.3,
   "end": 29.1,
   "text": "So that means they're 300 years older."
  },
  {
   "start": 29.28,
   "end": 31.08,
   "text": "And that's why they're green and this one's brown?"
  },
  {
   "start": 31.08,
   "end": 32.06,
   "text": "Yeah, that's bronze."
  },
  {
   "start": 32.38,
   "end": 33.38,
   "text": "So that's normal."
  },
  {
   "start": 33.52,
   "end": 34.92,
   "text": "Okay, and that's a normal material,"
  },
  {
   "start": 35.04,
   "end": 40.06,
   "text": "But it's quite an unusual choice to cast bells of steel."
  },
  {
   "start": 40.32,
   "end": 42.36,
   "text": "And this, the last great fire,"
  },
  {
   "start": 42.86,
   "end": 45.98,
   "text": "The old Tallinn actually burned down at the church also."
  },
  {
   "start": 46.18,
   "end": 47.38,
   "text": "It was in 1684."
  },
  {
   "start": 48.04,
   "end": 49.6,
   "text": "So the old bells melted."
  },
  {
   "start": 50.22,
   "end": 52.12,
   "text": "So they collected the old material"
  },
  {
   "start": 52.12,
   "end": 54.44,
   "text": "And recast the bells right here in Tallinn."
  },
  {
   "start": 54.78,
   "end": 56.38,
   "text": "So they actually did the second time."
  },
  {
   "start": 56.64,
   "end": 59.34,
   "text": "The second bell made of the same material."
  },
  {
   "start": 60.34,
   "end": 62.14,
   "text": "It was made by a German man,"
  },
  {
   "start": 62.14,
   "end": 64.86,
   "text": "But here in Estonia."
  },
  {
   "start": 64.98,
   "end": 67.32,
   "text": "There are actually two more bells up there."
  },
  {
   "start": 67.48,
   "end": 68.6,
   "text": "They are not so important,"
  },
  {
   "start": 69.1,
   "end": 70.66,
   "text": "But they are used every day,"
  },
  {
   "start": 71.0,
   "end": 72.08,
   "text": "Every hour, half hour."
  },
  {
   "start": 72.44,
   "end": 76.36,
   "text": "But these two are used only during Sunday mass"
  },
  {
   "start": 76.36,
   "end": 78.66,
   "text": "And weddings and funerals."
  },
  {
   "start": 78.66,
   "end": 80.9,
   "text": "Yeah, special occasions."
  },
  {
   "start": 81.46,
   "end": 83.3,
   "text": "This one has a crack in it."
  },
  {
   "start": 83.52,
   "end": 83.74,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 83.88,
   "end": 85.86,
   "text": "So they can't use this one right now."
  },
  {
   "start": 85.96,
   "end": 87.34,
   "text": "Oh, it'll break if they..."
  },
  {
   "start": 87.34,
   "end": 87.5,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 87.54,
   "end": 87.86,
   "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 87.98,
   "end": 88.52,
   "text": "Yeah, exactly."
  },
  {
   "start": 88.68,
   "end": 91.38,
   "text": "So they use the bell that's from 1685."
  },
  {
   "start": 91.7,
   "end": 91.92,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 92.52,
   "end": 94.06,
   "text": "And actually, this is the good one."
  },
  {
   "start": 94.24,
   "end": 95.06,
   "text": "We can..."
  },
  {
   "start": 95.06,
   "end": 96.7,
   "text": "That is actually not allowed,"
  },
  {
   "start": 96.86,
   "end": 98.02,
   "text": "But I don't care."
  },
  {
   "start": 98.02,
   "end": 100.94,
   "text": "So they have a completely..."
  },
  {
   "start": 100.94,
   "end": 103.32,
   "text": "Ah-ha."
  },
  {
   "start": 104.58,
   "end": 105.1,
   "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
   "start": 106.9,
   "end": 108.08,
   "text": "Completely different sound."
  },
  {
   "start": 108.28,
   "end": 108.96,
   "text": "Yeah, of course,"
  },
  {
   "start": 109.06,
   "end": 109.84,
   "text": "Material is different."
