  {
   "start": 110.02,
   "end": 110.58,
   "text": "Do-do."
  },
  {
   "start": 111.12,
   "end": 113.5,
   "text": "High pitch for the copper."
  },
  {
   "start": 113.68,
   "end": 114.12,
   "text": "That's cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 114.98,
   "end": 115.48,
   "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
   "start": 116.28,
   "end": 117.46,
   "text": "I guess if you were up here"
  },
  {
   "start": 117.46,
   "end": 118.46,
   "text": "While they went off,"
  },
  {
   "start": 118.54,
   "end": 119.36,
   "text": "You'd go deaf, huh?"
  },
  {
   "start": 119.46,
   "end": 120.08,
   "text": "Yeah, exactly."
  },
  {
   "start": 120.58,
   "end": 122.12,
   "text": "When you were up here,"
  },
  {
   "start": 122.32,
   "end": 123.36,
   "text": "You were just talking to them"
  },
  {
   "start": 123.36,
   "end": 125.86,
   "text": "When one of those two..."
  },
  {
   "start": 125.86,
   "end": 126.72,
   "text": "Well, just..."
  },
  {
   "start": 126.72,
   "end": 128.44,
   "text": "I don't know what time it is."
  },
  {
   "start": 128.54,
   "end": 129.26,
   "text": "It's..."
  },
  {
   "start": 129.26,
   "end": 131.56,
   "text": "Anyway, it's just..."
  },
  {
   "start": 131.56,
   "end": 132.66,
   "text": "It's a half hour."
  },
  {
   "start": 133.44,
   "end": 134.36,
   "text": "It's 2.30?"
  },
  {
   "start": 134.62,
   "end": 135.1,
   "text": "Yeah, exactly."
  },
  {
   "start": 135.22,
   "end": 136.42,
   "text": "So they just went off,"
  },
  {
   "start": 136.52,
   "end": 137.36,
   "text": "But you couldn't hear it"
  },
  {
   "start": 137.36,
   "end": 138.72,
   "text": "Because when you're up here,"
  },
  {
   "start": 139.04,
   "end": 140.96,
   "text": "You really practically can't hear it."
  },
  {
   "start": 141.4,
   "end": 142.46,
   "text": "When you're down on the ground,"
  },
  {
   "start": 142.56,
   "end": 144.14,
   "text": "You can hear it perfectly well"
  },
  {
   "start": 144.14,
   "end": 145.22,
   "text": "Because the sound travels."
  },
  {
   "start": 145.76,
   "end": 146.48,
   "text": "Like this."
  },
  {
   "start": 146.74,
   "end": 147.52,
   "text": "But when you're up here"
  },
  {
   "start": 147.52,
   "end": 148.44,
   "text": "And those..."
  },
  {
   "start": 148.44,
   "end": 148.74,
   "text": "Uh-huh."
  },
  {
   "start": 148.96,
   "end": 149.34,
   "text": "Then, yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 149.64,
   "end": 149.78,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 149.9,
   "end": 151.16,
   "text": "Because I happened to be,"
  },
  {
   "start": 151.22,
   "end": 151.7,
   "text": "Unfortunately,"
  },
  {
   "start": 151.98,
   "end": 153.26,
   "text": "Last Sunday."
  },
  {
   "start": 153.62,
   "end": 155.5,
   "text": "I didn't quite check my..."
  },
  {
   "start": 155.5,
   "end": 157.56,
   "text": "Times-wise was on that level."
  },
  {
   "start": 157.72,
   "end": 157.96,
   "text": "Uh-huh."
  },
  {
   "start": 158.02,
   "end": 158.54,
   "text": "Fortunately,"
  },
  {
   "start": 158.9,
   "end": 159.8,
   "text": "I was..."
  },
  {
   "start": 159.8,
   "end": 161.46,
   "text": "I just went running down."
  },
  {
   "start": 161.58,
   "end": 161.72,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 162.64,
   "end": 165.8,
   "text": "Oh, and this is the original hand"
  },
  {
   "start": 165.8,
   "end": 167.66,
   "text": "Of the clock from that side."
  },
  {
   "start": 167.88,
   "end": 168.4,
   "text": "Oh, okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 168.52,
   "end": 169.58,
   "text": "This is the original one"
  },
  {
   "start": 169.58,
   "end": 170.58,
   "text": "From the 18th..."
  },
  {
   "start": 170.58,
   "end": 171.94,
   "text": "From 1778."
  },
  {
   "start": 172.44,
   "end": 173.04,
   "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
   "start": 173.14,
   "end": 173.32,
   "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 173.8,
   "end": 174.96,
   "text": "You can see it works like this."
  },
  {
   "start": 174.96,
   "end": 175.46,
   "text": "Uh-huh."
  },
  {
   "start": 175.72,
   "end": 176.02,
   "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 176.16,
   "end": 177.36,
   "text": "This is the original one."
  },
  {
   "start": 177.58,
   "end": 179.18,
   "text": "And each face of the clock"
  },
  {
   "start": 179.18,
   "end": 180.3,
   "text": "Only has one hand."
  },
  {
   "start": 180.64,
   "end": 180.96,
   "text": "Uh-huh."
  },
  {
   "start": 181.14,
   "end": 182.72,
   "text": "No minutes, only hours."
  },
  {
   "start": 182.96,
   "end": 183.3,
   "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 183.38,
   "end": 183.86,
   "text": "And that's, again,"
  },
  {
   "start": 184.28,
   "end": 185.16,
   "text": "Well, the reason is"
  },
  {
   "start": 185.16,
   "end": 186.6,
   "text": "Because in the Middle Ages,"
  },
  {
   "start": 186.76,
